OL,5, A war veteran has paid out of his own  
OL,6, pocket to light up a war memorial for  
OL,7, Remembrance events.                    
OL,9,FJohn Davies, 39, from Aberystwyth, said
OL,10,Fit was about giving those who had lost 
OL,11,Ftheir lives the respect they deserve.  
OL,13,FIt has cost Mr Davies, who served in   
OL,14,FAfghanistan, about #3,500 for the      
OL,15,Flights and PA system around the town's 
OL,16,Fwar memorial.                          
OL,18,FCeredigion council said issues with    
OL,19,Ftheir own lighting system would be     
OL,20,Frepaired "as soon as possible".        
